
flowchart TD
    Start([START]) --> Init[Set system to ACTIVE status]
    Init --> Monitor[/Display: System is monitoring sensors/]
    
    %% Monitoring Loop [cite: 385, 401, 403]
    Monitor --> ReadSensors[Read Motion and Door/Window sensors]
    ReadSensors --> Detect{Is motion detected or a door open?}
    
    %% No Threat Path
    Detect -->|NO| ResetCheck
    
    %% Threat Detected Path [cite: 386, 387, 388]
    Detect -->|YES| ActivateCam[Activate security cameras and record]
    ActivateCam --> Homeowner{Is the homeowner present?}
    
    %% False Alarm Path [cite: 389]
    Homeowner -->|YES| FalseAlarm[/Display: False alarm. Homeowner recognized./]
    FalseAlarm --> ResetCheck
    
    %% True Threat Path [cite: 390, 391]
    Homeowner -->|NO| ThreatLevel{Determine threat level: 1, 2, or 3}
    ThreatLevel --> Notify[Send SMS, App, and Email notifications]
    Notify --> Siren[Trigger local alarm siren]
    Siren --> ResetCheck
    
    %% Reset and Loop [cite: 393, 408]
    ResetCheck{Has a reset command been received?}
    ResetCheck -->|YES| Deactivate[Stop siren and clear alarms]
    ResetCheck -->|NO| LoopWait[Wait for 5 seconds]
    
    Deactivate --> LoopWait
    LoopWait -->|Continue Monitoring| Monitor
